www.enanyang.my|language=zh-hans}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=峰会上用马来语演讲却没翻译，端依布拉欣挨批|url=https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/603101|access-date=2021-12-20|date=2021-12-15|work=Malaysiakini|archive-date=2021-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220083549/https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/603101|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

